<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>Geotechnical Engineering in San Diego</title><meta name="description" content="Geotechnical engineering and soil mechanics study services in San Diego. Advanced lab testing, in-situ characterization"><link rel="canonical" href="https://san-diego.geotechnicalengineering1.biz/"><meta property="og:type" content="website"><meta property="og:title" content="Geotechnical Engineering in San Diego"><meta property="og:description" content="Geotechnical engineering and soil mechanics study services in San Diego. Advanced lab testing, in-situ characterization"><meta property="og:url" content="https://san-diego.geotechnicalengineering1.biz/"><meta property="og:site_name" content="Geotechnicalengineering1"><meta property="og:image" content="https://san-diego.geotechnicalengineering1.biz/img/estudio-mecanica-suelos-1.webp"><meta property="og:locale" content="en_US"><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"><meta name="twitter:title" content="Geotechnical Engineering in San Diego"><meta name="twitter:description" content="Geotechnical engineering and soil mechanics study services in San Diego. Advanced lab testing, in-situ characterization, and foundation analysis per IBC and ASTM standards for coastal and seismic">
